title: Wall Street Breakfast May 11: Stock Futures Point Higher Ahead of Key Inflation Report
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Stock futures point higher ahead of key inflation report. U.S. gas prices surge to fresh new high, with no long-term relief seen. Cathie Wood: ‘We think we could be in a global recession’. Catch today’s WSB article here.
